      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does GST billing software replace my CA?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No. It dramatically cuts the time your CA spends on data entry and reconciliation, so they focus on tax planning and audits. Most CAs prefer clients who use proper billing software because returns become accurate."
